{"tid":2510189,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"（全面脫貧）獲余文樂捐贈衣物  中国四川貧困學童寫信致謝","createTime":"2021-04-30T03:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T03:53:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1dd1c5f2a8c9fabfe74f6eb67a3127b7d5f5ce00","tid":2510189,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:37:55.000Z","msg":"藝人余文樂早前以個人名義，捐贈逾300件衣物予四川貧困學童。當地學童日前收到衣物後興奮地即場試穿，並集體寫信感謝余文樂。<br />\n<br />\n根據內地傳媒報道，余文樂早前捐出一批其自家品牌的衣物，給四川省甘孜藏族自治州石渠縣的貧困學童，當中包括41件外衣、63條外褲及270件短袖上衣。學童收到該批衣物後感到非常興奮，並在老師協助下即場試穿。<br />\n<br />\n事後又集體寫信給余文樂，感謝其對他們的關心及支持，又指「將無法忘記您對貧困學生的幫助，今天我們滿懷感恩的心，對您表示我們最真誠的感謝！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/278cc173cd42e7a431a0c5ade0439d8c/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210430/_2021043010553841084.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F278cc173cd42e7a431a0c5ade0439d8c%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210430%2F_2021043010553841084.jpg&h=0781cd98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline .com/news/realtime /hk/2060613</code></pre>"},{"pid":"f6c089a00f5c942a7214c40f75a4cff44c4781ac","tid":2510189,"uid":234974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:44:00.000Z","msg":"習大親自部署親自指揮嘅全國脫貧攻堅戰已經勝利完成, 余文樂你有咩居心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd7788f1a9abc3c204595899ff90126cd043937","tid":2510189,"uid":378363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:53:01.000Z","msg":"佢咩居心，全民脫貧喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}